translations: （Dux）人名；（德、英、西、匈）杜克斯；（法）迪克斯

sentences.sentence: A large green tree-dwelling frog Litoria dux was discovered on the northern side of the Huon Peninsula a 16 500 sq km area of montane and lowland forest surrounded by ocean.
sentences.translation: 一种很大的绿色的树居的青蛙，雨滨蛙属，在胡昂半岛北部被发现。那里有面积达16500万平方公里被海洋包围的山地和洼地森林。
